r />\n<br />\n公屋唔養得狗係基本守規,你攞屋時應該好清楚,俾人扣分踢走係自己攞嚟...<br />\n<br />\n政府學呀爺咁鐵腕管治,連新年都唔俾小販賣吓嘢食賀年就大大力話要依法...<br />\n<br />\n呢啲長遠存在既問題就扮軟弱! <br />\n<br />\n至於你話啲狗俾人棄養呢啲問題更加係應該一早要諗...香港都唔係話無辦法處理流狼狗吖..<br />\n<br />\n加上每日都有動物俾人棄養,呢個根本唔係政府唔做嘢既理由,係一個大字:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">懶!</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"0929d1f5cda77fc1312ba7e589ed26caa2ac5fa0","tid":811952,"uid":56701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公屋戶同戶之間,根本係好近,狗啲氣味...其實好容易傳到去隔離戶...<br />\n<br />\n但啲養狗戶成日話唔影響人...你聞慣左啲狗屎狗尿味就話姐...人地住响你隔離想開大度門吹吓風都驚俾你隻狗搞到食唔落飯呀!</span>"},{"pid":"230b56d324299df0622e1f19e692ee51a7f84fc6","tid":811952,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"政府根本就係欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"27c908cac15da62e3143a4f882ca5aa3a2799cbe","tid":811952,"uid":80593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"809ec0ea2f2b87d95233de563c06f2a660efdd04","tid":811952,"uid":56701,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T09:17:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人每日做成十粒鐘...想話好好瞓一覺既人權都無...狗一吠一聲!你連睡意都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽朝仲要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n養狗賤戶仲會大大聲話:<br />\n我隻狗好撚賊乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無吠!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 